1052
01:22:08,428 --> 01:22:09,764
YOUNG SAM: <i>Thorp, what is that?</i>

1053
01:22:16,904 --> 01:22:18,405
[ELECTRICAL BUZZING]

1054
01:22:19,741 --> 01:22:21,475
[MUFFLED TALKING]

1055
01:22:21,508 --> 01:22:22,777
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

1056
01:22:23,711 --> 01:22:25,847
