1059
01:22:39,493 --> 01:22:41,161
[SINISTER MUSIC PLAYING]

1060
01:22:44,866 --> 01:22:46,366
[DISTANT SCREAMING]

1061
01:22:52,272 --> 01:22:58,445
After that, my parents battled
depression, drugs, insomnia.

1062
01:23:00,748 --> 01:23:01,682
[SNIFFLES]

1063
01:23:01,716 --> 01:23:05,385
We were trying to put
the past behind us.

1064
01:23:07,254 --> 01:23:09,724
<i>But my mother was haunted
by what happened.</i>

1065
01:23:11,859 --> 01:23:13,260
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

1066
01:23:16,563 --> 01:23:17,932
[CONTINUES BREATHING HEAVILY]

1067
01:23:20,500 --> 01:23:22,469
[GASPS, CRYING]

1068
01:23:25,439 --> 01:23:26,640
<i>Couldn't sleep.</i>

1069
01:23:27,008 --> 01:23:28,375
<i>Couldn't work.</i>

1070
01:23:32,546 --> 01:23:34,448
Nobody believed her, though.

1071
01:23:34,481 --> 01:23:35,950
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

1072
01:23:44,291 --> 01:23:45,960
And in the end,
that's what did it.

1073
01:23:49,429 --> 01:23:50,798
Nobody believed her.

1074
01:24:09,449 --> 01:24:10,684
[YOUNG SAM SCREAMING]

1075
01:24:17,457 --> 01:24:19,727
My father said
he wouldn't be selfish...

1076
01:24:20,260 --> 01:24:21,896
that he'd look after me.

1077
01:24:24,899 --> 01:24:26,666
<i>But he couldn't take the shame.</i>

1078
01:24:29,070 --> 01:24:31,939
And on the anniversary
of my mother's death...

1079
01:24:54,061 --> 01:24:55,495
[WEAKLY] I'm sorry.

1080
01:24:57,098 --> 01:24:58,632
Where are your parents?

1081
01:24:59,801 --> 01:25:01,035
They won't come back.

1082
01:25:03,403 --> 01:25:05,405
There's nothing on Earth
worth their time.

1083
01:25:07,674 --> 01:25:09,744
They told me not to
come and find you.

1084
01:25:09,777 --> 01:25:12,546
You got to say goodbye
to your family.

1085
01:25:13,380 --> 01:25:14,514
I never did.

1086
01:25:14,548 --> 01:25:16,851
We were so small
when it happened.

1087
01:25:20,420 --> 01:25:22,056
I never wanted to hurt you.

1088
01:25:22,723 --> 01:25:23,825
[SOBS]

1089
01:25:24,926 --> 01:25:26,828
Somehow...

1090
01:25:26,861 --> 01:25:30,131
Unbelievably,
I had fun again.

1091
01:25:30,164 --> 01:25:31,933
Like when we were kids.

1092
01:25:32,834 --> 01:25:33,935
When I loved you.

1093
01:25:34,769 --> 01:25:36,070
[GASPS, SOBS]

1094
01:25:36,103 --> 01:25:37,337
[GRUNTS]

1095
01:25:39,506 --> 01:25:41,008
