1123
01:31:51,078 --> 01:31:52,179
Shit!

1124
01:31:59,086 --> 01:32:00,421
Junior?

1125
01:32:00,454 --> 01:32:01,855
[CROW CAWING]

1126
01:32:16,837 --> 01:32:17,871
[EXHALES]

1127
01:32:21,442 --> 01:32:23,110
Are you Pauline?

1128
01:32:37,858 --> 01:32:39,460
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

1129
01:33:00,981 --> 01:33:02,049
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

1130
01:33:29,243 --> 01:33:30,377
Olivia.

1131
01:33:33,347 --> 01:33:36,950
Okay. Guess I'll have to eat
all this ice cream by myself.

1132
